@startuml
title BP-26 - Cash Payment through Finance Officer

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Receive cash payment from parent or student;
:Search student outstanding bills;
:Select obligations to settle;
:Input received cash amount;

|Platform|
:Validate finance role;
:Validate student belongs to tenant;
:Validate amount is greater than zero;
:Create PaymentOrder with CASH method;
:Create payment allocations;
:Update obligation outstanding balances;

if (Order fully allocated?) then (Yes)
  :Set PaymentOrder status to COMPLETED;
  :Post ledger debit to Cash account;
  :Post credit to revenue accounts;
else (No)
  :Keep PaymentOrder status as PENDING;
endif

|Finance Officer|
:Print or show payment receipt;
stop

note right
Current MVP supports CASH as PaymentOrder method.
Ledger posting happens when order becomes COMPLETED.
end note
@enduml
